snippet.title: Arcade Archives Soldier Girl Amazon
snippet.description:
"Soldier Girl Amazon" is a shooting game released by Nihon Bussan in 1986.
Amazon—a female warrior—fights on earth where it is now dominated by strange beasts and frantic cyborgs.
Get a hold of the enemy's aero mobile and track down the prisoner group that has escaped from a certain star in the universe.

Arcade Archives Official Website
http://www.hamster.co.jp/american_hamster/arcadearchives/
